# SWIM Architecture - CRITICAL RULES

## Communication Flow - NEVER FORGET

```
┌─────────────────┐         AMQP          ┌─────────────────┐
│   MOCKSERVER    │ ───────────────────── │    CONSUMER     │
│  (EAD Simulator)│    publishes events   │  (ANSP Client)  │
└─────────────────┘                       └─────────────────┘
                                                   │
                                                   │ Kafka
                                                   ▼
                                          ┌─────────────────┐
                                          │  Kafka Topics   │
                                          └─────────────────┘

┌─────────────────┐         AMQP          ┌─────────────────┐
│    PROVIDER     │ ───────────────────── │   MOCKCLIENT    │
│ (AISP Simulator)│    publishes events   │  (Test Client)  │
└─────────────────┘                       └─────────────────┘
```

## ABSOLUTE RULES

1. **Consumer** connects to **MockServer** via AMQP
   - Consumer is the AMQP client
   - MockServer (Artemis) is the AMQP broker

2. **MockClient** connects to **Provider** via AMQP
   - MockClient is the AMQP client
   - Provider (Artemis) is the AMQP broker

3. **Consumer and Provider DO NOT communicate directly**
   - NO direct connection between them
   - They are independent systems
   - The only shared resource could be Kafka (for downstream processing)

4. **When Consumer has AMQP issues:**
   - Check MockServer/Artemis status
   - DO NOT check Provider

5. **When MockClient has AMQP issues:**
   - Check Provider/Artemis status
   - DO NOT check MockServer

## Component Mapping

| Component | Role | Connects To |
|-----------|------|-------------|
| swim-dnotam-consumer | ANSP Consumer | swim-dnotam-mockserver (Artemis) |
| swim-dnotam-mockserver | EAD Simulator | N/A (is the broker) |
| swim-dnotam-provider | AISP Provider | N/A (is the broker) |
| swim-dnotam-mockclient | Test Client | swim-dnotam-provider (Artemis) |

## Namespace: swim-sandbox

| Pod | Purpose |
|-----|---------|
| swim-dnotam-consumer-0 | Consumes DNOTAM from MockServer |
| swim-dnotam-provider-* | Provides DNOTAM to MockClient |
| provider-artemis-ss-0 | Artemis broker for Provider |
| mongodb-* | Event persistence |
| kafka-* | Downstream event streaming |
